        {
            "title": "A股偏軟  滬股跌深股升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股低開後竹土口大卜穩，滬股跑輸，深股報升。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證指數開報4043點，跌0.3%或12點。現跌11點或0.27%，報4044點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開報14806點，漲0.07%或10點。現升15點或0.11，報14811</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指開報3643點，漲0.47%或17點。升8點或0.22%，報3634點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300開報4729點，跌0.16%或7點。現跌10點或0.23%，報4726點。</p>\n</div>",
